result.longName: Aqar Real Estate Investments Company - K.S.C. (Public)

assetProfile.address2: Al Qibla Square Tower, 30th Floor Al Qibla, Street 23 PO Box 20017
assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Aqar Real Estate Investments Company - K.S.C. (Public), together with its subsidiaries, engages in the real estate business in Kuwait and internationally. The company operates through Real Estate, Investments, and Other segments. It also develops, buys, and sells properties; rent and lease properties; manages third party properties; invest in financial portfolios; establishes, manages, leases, and sells buildings and real estate projects, residential and commercial complexes, private and public parking lots; offers economic, technical, and engineering studies and consultations related to real estate business, and private and public real estate projects; and acquire, buy, and sells share and bonds of real estate companies. In addition, the company provides maintenance work related to building and real estate; acquires and manages, rents, and leases hotels, health clubs, tourist utilities, motels, hospitality and rest houses, park, garden, exhibition, restaurants, cafeterias, housing complex, and entertainment and sports projects; and organize real estate auctions. Further, it establishes and manages real estate investment funds; imports building materials; builds, operates, and transfers infrastructure of district, residential, commercial, and environmental industrial projects through system; and manages real estate utilities. The company was incorporated in 1997 and is based in Kuwait City, Kuwait.
